Looking for a Volkswagen Jetta near Washington?

The Volkswagen Jetta gives buyers the best of all worlds-- carefully packaging features and tweaking the Jetta's price level. Volkswagen wants buyers to feel they can get a premium German sedan or wagon at a friendly price, with fit and finish similar to that on cars that cost two and three times as much. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect Jetta for you.

Autotrader has 23,944 Volkswagen Jettas for sale near Washington, DC, including a Certified 2016 Volkswagen Jetta SEL Sedan w/ Lighting Package, a Certified 2017 Volkswagen Jetta, and a Certified 2017 Volkswagen Jetta GLI SE Sedan.

Not sure if a Jetta is the right fit for you?

That's okay! We make it easy to shop for your next vehicle by body type, mileage, price, and much more.You can find other popular Volkswagen vehicles such as Tiguan, Passat, and GTI on Autotrader.
